<!--
  Sparkle appcast for Beaver. Lives on the gh-pages branch (or under
  /docs on main; see DECISIONS.md D22) at:

      https://applicaster.github.io/Beaver/appcast.xml

  Sparkle in installed Beaver instances polls this URL once per
  startup (and again every 24h) to discover available updates.

  Each release adds one <item> to this file. The CI release job runs
  Sparkle's `sign_update` on the produced .zip, captures the Ed25519
  signature, and appends a fresh <item> here automatically — see
  scripts/release.sh.

  Seed state: empty. The first 1.0.0 release is on GitHub Releases
  but is not in the appcast (was published before Sparkle landed),
  so users on 1.0.0 will need to do one manual upgrade to get the
  auto-update channel. From 1.1.0 onward, updates are automatic.
-->
